When this Equipment enters, return target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield. Attach this Equipment to that creature.
Equipped creature has base power and toughness 4/4, has flying and vigilance, and is an Angel in addition to its other types.
Equip {4}

Equipped creature gets +2/+2 and has protection from lands and from legendary sources.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, it deals damage to that player equal to the number of nonbasic lands that player controls and you create a colorless land token named Everywhere that is every basic land type.
